{"tid":1329001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要唔分化 張超雄都要負責","createTime":"2019-07-18T05:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:51:26.000Z","uid":236709,"like":57,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"600eeb578becb9d9a6397e298936dbee1f883139","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"我唔當張超雄係鬼定唔鬼<br />\n但唔割蓆，唔單止係我地要收聲<br />\n佢自己都要收番佢咁有爭議既提案<br />\n<br />\n無論呢一個提案對呢一個運動好與壞<br />\n只要提案有爭議<br />\n都會令到我哋容易分裂<br />\n係不分化不割蓆呢一個前提下<br />\n身為張超雄收番條提案係應該<br />\n唔係連登仔單方面收聲唔屌你<br />\n<br />\n我呢個睇法唔知啱唔啱<br />\n但無論點都好7月21號大家不見不散"},{"pid":"e0b571e26a2a51e8516192a403dc8c16cc35c74e","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba790e5c5a5c526caaf781f0d96ed24a80bf2996","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Push</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b6417b67c08a26d7bbedf6818507224a407167bf","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"26fc961bcc4f86dd3db680c8dab23b179f2e9189","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"89c1c848bf4a5695990fb512b1a3a7696043335b","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8daee81d9f9c413ab3b7c9c10427a7d8bf82727e","tid":1329001,"uid":28279,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"對事不對人，佢應該收返"},{"pid":"b0c048d61a893f0f5feddea4f806a24351216296","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2f154b2f7926a4535d94a956a84cfe683aee1414","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c00b5a0adae141d3927c1ffcdc2b29b36ae06cec","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<del></del>"},{"pid":"90eaa34b6e99da906188dccd8bc8dd84cfdf59d6","tid":1329001,"uid":111150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4333cfb63545628ef99789a2e32776fb7a787c8f","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<del></del></blockquote>"},{"pid":"08401afed2bea2b8744340cab26cc1aa367d8842","tid":1329001,"uid":862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"RIGHT ATTITUDE"},{"pid":"ce9a3bb028b4c6aa07326b5f6f264a993d91b4ba","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<del></del></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"26d21ef446246a45b7e269c367eb6d5aad2244e5","tid":1329001,"uid":262228,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"梁啟智：【究竟張超雄想搞乜？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. 張超雄想搞乜？<br />\n<br />\n解決陳同佳案，將林鄭軍，等佢冇得再講初心乜乜乜。<br />\n<br />\n大家睇完個flowchart，應該理解到現行法例入面，要將疑犯由香港移交去第二個政府，係分長期協議同個案形式。而無論長期協議同個案，都 1) 要經立法會，同埋 2) 唔包中華人民共和國。政府原本個建議，係個案唔洗經立法會同埋包中華人民共和國（所以包台灣）。大家一路反對緊的，係政府呢個建議。<br />\n<br />\n咁「超雄方案」呢？現行法例乜都唔改，只係改一條：將唔包「中華人民共和國」變成唔包「中央人民政府或澳門政府」。換言之，台灣政府就得。<br />\n<br />\n如果通過咗「超雄方案」，就可以由台灣政府提出，然後香港政府同立法會審議，再然後送疑犯去台灣，in this case陳同佳。<br />\n<br />\n2. 台灣咪話咗唔受囉？<br />\n<br />\n台灣唔受的係政府方案，因為政府方案將台灣當係中國一部分處理。「超雄方案」同政府方案響呢方面剛剛相反，攞走現行法例中矮化台灣的寫法，對台灣係好事。<br />\n<br />\n3. 會唔會變成幫政府捉去咗台灣的手足？<br />\n<br />\n唔會。首先，條例係處理緊香港送人出去，唔係台灣送人來香港，出同入係兩件事來的。<br />\n<br />\n而如果台灣要送香港手足返香港，得兩個可能：1) 手足響台灣係訪客，咁台灣其實從來幾時都可以驅逐佢出境，唔關香港法例事；2) 手足響台灣入咗籍，咁更加唔可能，因為台灣本身有政策唔會送自己居民出去，亦唔關香港法例事。<br />\n<br />\n4. 台灣有死刑，送人去台灣係咪合理化日後可以送人去有酷刑的國家？<br />\n<br />\n唔會。現行法例寫明，送人前當地要保證唔會尋求死刑，去全世界邊個國家都係咁，而呢個保證亦要經過香港立法會審查。<br />\n<br />\n5. 佢好心地姐，但係建制派可能會改佢個修訂，改到面目全非呢？人地票數多喎！<br />\n<br />\n張超雄到時可以成條草案撤回，咁建制派在選民面前會變成真真正正導致不能解決陳同佳案的黑手。（大家真係要熟讀會議規則呀！）<br />\n<br />\n6. 點解呢個時候先提？會唔會幫咗林鄭？<br />\n<br />\n點會？林鄭咁鍾意講初心，就用初心將佢軍囉。建制派咁鍾意講守法，就迫佢地響法律面前表態囉。<br />\n<br />\n講好兄弟爬山，用立法會迫對家自相矛盾都係爬山方法的一種。大家可以對不同爬山方法有不同意見，好應該互相提點，但記住唔好切割呀⋯⋯"},{"pid":"7a179e199df19b9d4e407c64d4239a2276eafd39","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Push</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<del></del></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<ins></ins></blockquote>"},{"pid":"105a9c32e6a7faf44f7a2c9301b399976a6b1d71","tid":1329001,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"721 對準政權 五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1inJD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1inJD7.png&h=d1a99292&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jH96qSs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjH96qSs.png&h=a893231e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1f36b04c5ca5016307f078e2adc3d6b6acf9b44","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>721 對準政權 五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1inJD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1inJD7.png&h=d1a99292&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jH96qSs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjH96qSs.png&h=a893231e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5096c853e95dc839406d59821b4e3934fde354","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26d21ef446246a45b7e269c367eb6d5aad2244e5","tid":1329001,"uid":262228,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"梁啟智：【究竟張超雄想搞乜？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. 張超雄想搞乜？<br />\n<br />\n解決陳同佳案，將林鄭軍，等佢冇得再講初心乜乜乜。<br />\n<br />\n大家睇完個flowchart，應該理解到現行法例入面，要將疑犯由香港移交去第二個政府，係分長期協議同個案形式。而無論長期協議同個案，都 1) 要經立法會，同埋 2) 唔包中華人民共和國。政府原本個建議，係個案唔洗經立法會同埋包中華人民共和國（所以包台灣）。大家一路反對緊的，係政府呢個建議。<br />\n<br />\n咁「超雄方案」呢？現行法例乜都唔改，只係改一條：將唔包「中華人民共和國」變成唔包「中央人民政府或澳門政府」。換言之，台灣政府就得。<br />\n<br />\n如果通過咗「超雄方案」，就可以由台灣政府提出，然後香港政府同立法會審議，再然後送疑犯去台灣，in this case陳同佳。<br />\n<br />\n2. 台灣咪話咗唔受囉？<br />\n<br />\n台灣唔受的係政府方案，因為政府方案將台灣當係中國一部分處理。「超雄方案」同政府方案響呢方面剛剛相反，攞走現行法例中矮化台灣的寫法，對台灣係好事。<br />\n<br />\n3. 會唔會變成幫政府捉去咗台灣的手足？<br />\n<br />\n唔會。首先，條例係處理緊香港送人出去，唔係台灣送人來香港，出同入係兩件事來的。<br />\n<br />\n而如果台灣要送香港手足返香港，得兩個可能：1) 手足響台灣係訪客，咁台灣其實從來幾時都可以驅逐佢出境，唔關香港法例事；2) 手足響台灣入咗籍，咁更加唔可能，因為台灣本身有政策唔會送自己居民出去，亦唔關香港法例事。<br />\n<br />\n4. 台灣有死刑，送人去台灣係咪合理化日後可以送人去有酷刑的國家？<br />\n<br />\n唔會。現行法例寫明，送人前當地要保證唔會尋求死刑，去全世界邊個國家都係咁，而呢個保證亦要經過香港立法會審查。<br />\n<br />\n5. 佢好心地姐，但係建制派可能會改佢個修訂，改到面目全非呢？人地票數多喎！<br />\n<br />\n張超雄到時可以成條草案撤回，咁建制派在選民面前會變成真真正正導致不能解決陳同佳案的黑手。（大家真係要熟讀會議規則呀！）<br />\n<br />\n6. 點解呢個時候先提？會唔會幫咗林鄭？<br />\n<br />\n點會？林鄭咁鍾意講初心，就用初心將佢軍囉。建制派咁鍾意講守法，就迫佢地響法律面前表態囉。<br />\n<br />\n講好兄弟爬山，用立法會迫對家自相矛盾都係爬山方法的一種。大家可以對不同爬山方法有不同意見，好應該互相提點，但記住唔好切割呀⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:54:09.000Z","msg":"冇謂再針佢條野高唔高章<br />\n問題係今次真係有分化<br />\n而有一邊又真係唔gur<br />\n再咁就不功自破"},{"pid":"3510214323fdef075567aef1e5bd1b35a502d228","tid":1329001,"uid":215634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"實我覺得佢冇做錯，佢都係想打擊林鄭嘅初心論姐"},{"pid":"da491854457b76c97e8874e06c2d40146e4e3709","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3510214323fdef075567aef1e5bd1b35a502d228","tid":1329001,"uid":215634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"實我覺得佢冇做錯，佢都係想打擊林鄭嘅初心論姐"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"成本太高<br />\n搞到我地都自我分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525a02e8042b12a0528dbf8ae7d82fd1aaceac2b","tid":1329001,"uid":277667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"佢有佢提<br />\n照行<br />\n<br />\n撤回暴動定義<br />\n撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n追究警隊濫權<br />\n立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"466096c8c9a08173fa8c38f70aafe365963a4e22","tid":1329001,"uid":173936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"！唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘！<br />\n<br />\n721主線任務：<br />\n1. 立即撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 除消暴動定義<br />\n3. 不再追究義士<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查<br />\n5. 真雙普選<br />\n<br />\n香港人，靠自己！"},{"pid":"5b72213cea0066b274090991da9ea88b720bf04e","tid":1329001,"uid":16034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da491854457b76c97e8874e06c2d40146e4e3709","tid":1329001,"uid":236709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3510214323fdef075567aef1e5bd1b35a502d228","tid":1329001,"uid":215634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"實我覺得佢冇做錯，佢都係想打擊林鄭嘅初心論姐"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"成本太高<br />\n搞到我地都自我分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只可以講泛民＋議員定位就係咁，我支持張超雄收返個議案，你要搞修正案可以以後先搞，呢一刻唔應該分散左注意力<br />\n不過我又唔會話係分化嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲蠢咁囉"},{"pid":"e3c4f4ba4e624b2234ce35583d0b8557cd6b8e60","tid":1329001,"uid":124859,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"岩呀, 仲有收埋糾察隊呀屌 唔想又14年咁<br />\n泛民咩都唔好做就係最好做法"}]}